import React from 'react'
import { Row,Form,Button,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

const FormInput = () => {
  return (
   <Row>
    
       <Col sm="5">
         <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="ادخل سؤال" />
       </Col>
       <Col sm="5">
         <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="ادخل الاجابه" />
       </Col>
      <Col sm="2">
      <Button sm="4" className="btn-color" type="submit">
        اضافه
      </Button>
      </Col>
   </Row>
  )
}

export default FormInput
